I... I thought you would come over in the afternoon.

16
00:02:23,427 --> 00:02:25,847
I got something later. So I came early.

17
00:02:25,847 --> 00:02:30,647
- How about I... I'll leave. 
 - It's okay. I... I'm done here.

18
00:02:43,407 --> 00:02:44,647
I'm sorry.

19
00:02:44,647 --> 00:02:48,247
You broke up with me. So don't say sorry to me.

20
00:02:49,027 --> 00:02:52,107
I've been thinking these days

21
00:02:52,107 --> 00:02:55,107
about where I went wrong exactly.

22
00:02:55,107 --> 00:02:57,847
Later on, I figured it out.

23
00:02:57,847 --> 00:03:00,367
Actually, I didn't do anything wrong.

24
00:03:00,987 --> 00:03:07,067
It's not that only a long-term relationship is a good kind of love.

25
00:03:07,067 --> 00:03:11,827
Getting off halfway just means the journey has changed.

26
00:03:11,827 --> 00:03:15,087
It's not like we are going to be in love just once in our lives.

27
00:03:15,087 --> 00:03:18,827
Maybe there are many more breakups waiting for us.

28
00:03:40,727 --> 00:03:42,687
I'm taking this away.

29
00:03:42,687 --> 00:03:46,327
After all, our relationship was pretty good until it ended.

30
00:04:14,147 --> 00:04:15,887
I'll walk you out.

31
00:04:16,967 --> 00:04:21,587
Since we've already broken up, you should act like it.

32
00:04:21,587 --> 00:04:25,247
I can face it. Goodbye.

33
